        "data": "<h1 id=\"01H8066N1X71BMWR8KPQVMTM4A\">Service Updates for Liferay Cloud</h1>\n\n<p>The services update for&nbsp;<strong>2026-06-23</strong>&nbsp;includes&nbsp;<b>minor</b>&nbsp;updates for the <strong>Liferay&nbsp;</strong>and <strong>Webserver&nbsp;</strong>services.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1X678XQSM8P38E9Q5Z\">DXP Cloud Stack&nbsp;</h2>\n\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-color: #f7f8f9; border-spacing: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 100%;\">\n\t<colgroup>\n\t\t<col style=\"width: 16%;\">\n\t\t<col style=\"width: 14%;\">\n\t\t<col style=\"width: 13%;\">\n\t\t<col style=\"width: 57%;\">\n\t</colgroup>\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(150, 153, 150); padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></th>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(150, 153, 150); padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center;\"><strong>Previous Release</strong></th>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(150, 153, 150); padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center;\"><strong>Current Release</strong></th>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(150, 153, 150); padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center;\"><strong>Docker Images</strong></th>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 48px;\">\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">Backup</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">5.34.0</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">5.35.0</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>liferaycloud/backup:5.35.0</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">CI</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">6.6.0</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">6.7.0</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>liferaycloud/jenkins:2.555.3-lts-jdk21-6.7.0</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 41.2222px;\">\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">Database</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">5.13.0</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">5.14.0</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>liferaycloud/database:5.14.0</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Liferay</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>5.11.0</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>5.12.0</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li><strong>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.4-5.12.0</strong></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><strong>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.3-5.12.0</strong></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><strong>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2-5.12.0</strong></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><strong>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.1-5.12.0</strong></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">Search</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">5.7.0</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">5.8.0</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>liferaycloud/elasticsearch:8.19.16-5.8.0</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Webserver</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>6.8.0</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>6.9.0</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li><strong>liferaycloud/nginx:1.31.2-6.9.0</strong></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1YWTXV16JYNYMDV6F4\">Change Log</h2>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 93%;\">\n\t<colgroup>\n\t\t<col style=\"width: 15%;\">\n\t\t<col style=\"width: 14%;\">\n\t\t<col style=\"width: 14%;\">\n\t\t<col style=\"width: 57%;\">\n\t</colgroup>\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></th>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center;\"><strong>Service Version</strong></th>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center;\"><strong>Ticket No.</strong></th>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center;\"><strong>Description</strong></th>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n\t\t\t<p><b>Liferay</b></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>5.12.0</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;\"><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-52140\">LCD-52140</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Internal</strong>: Pipeline improvements</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;\"><b>Webserver</b></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>6.9.0</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n\t\t\t<p><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-52281\">LCD-52281</a></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n\t\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Internal</strong>: Pipeline improvements</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01HFQQE47127T9RVN8YK7MKH4R\">Update Instructions</h2>\n\n<p><strong>Note</strong>&nbsp;: To take advantage of the new features and fixes provided by the 5.x stack of services, you must update your entire stack to the new 5.x images or above.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1YDXGGCTPJ2C2XKQWE\">Image Update Instructions</h2>\n\n<p>The Liferay Cloud image versions needs to be set inside of the &lt;service&gt;/LCP.json file.</p>\n\n<p>Note, however, that the liferay service uses two image properties. The DXP Cloud image is set in the liferay/LCP.json file, but the liferay/dxp image is set in the gradle.properties. This change was made in order to facilitate easier deployment using the Liferay Cloud CLI.</p>\n\n<p>liferay/LCP.json file would set the liferaycloud/liferay-dxp image:&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"overflow-auto portlet-msg-info\">\"image\":\"liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.4-5.X.X\"</div>\n\n<p>liferay/gradle.properties file would set the liferay/dxp image:</p>\n\n<div class=\"overflow-auto portlet-msg-info\">liferay.workspace.docker.image.liferay=liferay/dxp:2024.q1.1</div>\n\n<p>For all other images, you will just need to update the LCP.json file with the intended image version.</p>\n\n<p>Once the LCP.json files are updated, commit the changes to your Git repository.</p>\n\n<div class=\"overflow-auto portlet-msg-info\">git add . &amp;&amp; git commit -m \"Update dxp cloud stack to XXX\"</div>\n\n<p>After pushing these changes to the remote repository, a build will be created in Liferay Cloud and it is ready to deploy.</p>"
      },
